<db:para>This page shows some of the widgets available in Qt when configured to use the &quot;windowsvista&quot; style. This style is only available on Windows Vista or later. This style provides native look'n'feel by integrating to the Windows platform theme. Thus, the final appearance varies depending on the active Windows theme.</db:para>
